## Difficulty

[Bitcoin Difficulty increased yesterday!](https://bitcoinwisdom.com/bitcoin/difficulty): 46684376316

This invalidates our results from the previous class about the SP20
miner being profitable (with our assumption about 5% difficulty increase
per month). 

PointCoin's difficulty rate reveals something about when students got
their miners working, and about how EC2 throttles micro instances:

